import React from 'react'
  import { MDXTag } from '@mdx-js/tag'
  import { Playground, PropsTable } from "docz"
import Action from "../components/Action"

export default ({components, ...props}) => <MDXTag name="wrapper"  components={components}>

<MDXTag name="h1" components={components} props={{"id":"action"}}><MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="h1" props={{"aria-hidden":true,"href":"#action"}}><MDXTag name="span" components={components} parentName="a" props={{"className":"icon-link"}}>{`#`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>{`Action`}</MDXTag>
<Playground __position={0} __code={`<Action>My Action</Action>`} __scope={{props,Action}}>
    <Action>My Action</Action>
</Playground>
<PropsTable of={ Action }/></MDXTag>
